name: Rhino GOO! Fast Action Cleaner - 5 LTR
description:
RhinoGoo Fast Action Cleaner is a unique blend of fully biodegradable chemicals which are designed to clean every part of your Vehicle.

RhinoGoo is especially tough on brake dust and very mild on more delicate components. It’s totally safe on anodising, aluminum, paintwork, suspension seals, rubber, disc brake pads, carbon fibre and fibre glass. 

With its unique dirt removing formula and superb results you will wonder how you ever managed without it! Simply hose down the machine, spray RhinoGoo all over, leave for a minute and then hose off for a super clean finish. 

Rhino Goo is non irritant, fully bio-degradable, Non Caustic, Aluminum friendly and meets all new EU guidelines and regulations.

All RhinoGoo products are manufactured to the highest specification using only the finest chemical solutions sourced in the UK and are extensively tested prior to being marketed through our distribution network.
